bibliothek.gui.dock.facile.menu

Class FreeMenuPiece

  • java.lang.Object
    • bibliothek.gui.dock.support.menu.MenuPiece
      • bibliothek.gui.dock.support.menu.BaseMenuPiece
        • bibliothek.gui.dock.facile.menu.FreeMenuPiece

  • @ClientOnly
public class FreeMenuPiece
extends BaseMenuPiece
    A MenuPiece that does not add any children by itself. All items have to be added or removed directly by the client.
    Author:
    Benjamin Sigg
